channel.title: Commands help
channel.description:
Well, I just finily finished my server using a Allstarscape Source V2, and now I can't find anything telling me the commands. Could someone post a link to a complete list of commands for Allstar V2?
Also, when ever I try to do ::giveadmin or ::givemod, it always tells me their offline, even though their on.

item.title: Commands help
item.dc:creator: @Mod-Vlad Mod-Vlad-
item.description:
@Mod-Vlad wrote:

This is probably easiest thing on Allstar.
You firstly must know right amount and right letters and numbers of a nickname, all spaces, symbols. Then I must tell you a one thing of an Allstar - you cannot do ::give— commands twice per log in. Log in once, do ::give— “nickname”, it must work, then log out, and log on back, must work against.

Read full topic
